text: Erna Rahbek Pedersen was an archer from Denmark. She was born on 6 October 1926 and died in 2002. Pedersen competed at the 1972 Summer Olympics.Erna Rahbek Pedersen == References == Category:1926 births Category:2002 deaths Category:Danish archers Category:Olympians for Denmark
